<h1 id="create-a-leave-request-workflow" sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Create a leave request workflow</h1>

<p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">You can create a workflow in Dynamics 365 Human Resources to consistently manage your leave and absence requests. A <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Leave and absence</strong> workflow lets you:</p>
<ul sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Define tasks</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="37">Determine who must complete the tasks</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Specify who can approve or reject requests</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="create-a-leave-and-absence-request-workflow" sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Create a Leave and absence request workflow</h2>
<ol sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Leave and absence</strong> page, select the <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Links</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Under <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Setup</strong>, select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Human resource workflows</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">New</strong>, and then select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Leave and absence request</strong>.</p>
