<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">When the <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Open this file?</strong> message box appears, select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Open</strong> and sign in with your company credentials.</p>
