<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Use the workflow editor to create a workflow for your leave requests. For more information about working with workflows, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dynamics365/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/create-workflow?toc=/dynamics365/commerce/toc.json." sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Create workflows overview</a></p>
